| C.4 ★ | Profile verbalization | Which profile variables are encoded and exactly how they are rendered into text — fixed template vs. LLM-generated persona narratives (if the latter: the generating model and prompt, recursively subject to this form). |
| C.5 ★ | Assignment & weighting | Number of personas, assignment to conditions (between- vs. within-subjects), reuse across conditions, and any weighting or matching to a target population. |

