| Item | Name | What to report |
|---|---|--------|
| G.1 | Competing interests | Funding, in-kind compute or model access, and professional or financial relationships with entities that have an interest in LLMs — particularly relevant where teams evaluate models built by affiliated organizations. |
| G.2 ★ | External human data | A self-declared list of all external human datasets that informed the approach anywhere (training, fine-tuning, retrieval, in-context examples, calibration anchors) — particularly published trust-in-science or climate-communication experiments. |
