One row per synthetic respondent, matching the structure of the cleaned analysis data (`cleaned_llm.rds` schema). Teams are strongly encouraged to use the published profile pool with its fixed condition assignments (N = 9,000), so that `profile_id` links submissions across teams; deviations must be registered under C.3/C.5.

